<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="for-the-sake-of-sb-sth">for the sake of sb / sth</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-for-sbs-sths-sake">1.<strong>为了某人 / 某事物的缘故 (for sb’s / sth’s sake):</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He moved to the seaside for the sake of his health. 
他为了健康而搬去海边。</p></div></div>